posting_body: ['❤Pet-Friendly South Lamar 1x1!', '❤', '*If you sign up with our preferred renters insurance provider, ePremium, we can waive $100 off the security deposit, as well as waive the $200 pet deposits if you have pets!', '🐾 Mention this ad!*', 'APARTMENT', 'Pictures are of actual unit - available September✓', 'You will have 622 sqft and a covered private patio!', 'The unit is located on the first floor and is going for $1495/month.', "The apartment is Google Fiber-ready with a jack, but if you'd like to opt for a different provider feel free!", 'Water is allocated (usually about $25/person) and electricity is set up through the City of Austin.', 'Only $1/wash and $1/dry at our 24/7 on-site laundry facility!', 'COMMUNITY', 'No breed restrictions/weight limits', 'Off leash dog park', 'Swimming pool', 'Property security', 'Near transportation + very walkable!', 'Laundry Facility on site', '24/7 maintenance', 'Guest parking', 'Off-street parking', 'Covered balcony', 'Popular area by South Lamar', 'Private and tucked away location!', 'Contact info:', 'Zoee', 'Tramor at Creek Village & Quest', 'show contact info', 'or Cell:', 'show contact info']
